         <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">Author; Travel writer; Feminist; Suffragist; and Relief worker, World War I.  Includes printed material, correspondence, published writings and typescripts, memorabilia, notes, photographs, and organization files. Information relating to the International Council of Women, the National Council of Women, and the Montessori Education Association of New York.
